Package fr.polytechtours.prd.multiagent.heuristic.meta

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Calculate
    Interface Calculate to provide calculate service
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constant
    All constants as configuration of NSGA2
    CrowdingDistanceAssignment
    This class provides methods to calculate the crowding distances for individuals
    Individual
    Individual to simulation one solution of NSGA2
    One individual contains : genes: its genes of size N with 0 for scheduled and 1 for abandoned fitness: values of objective functions number dominated: the number of individuals which dominates this individual set dominant: set of individuals which this individual dominates crowdedDistance: crowded distance valid: if this individual is feasible or not
    NondominatedSetConstructor
    This class provides methods to sort the population by their level of dominant
    In return, several sets are returned in order of their rank of dominant
    The lower rank comes first
    NSGA2
    This class provides the main loop and several global methods for NSGA2.
    SubSetCalculator  
    TestNSGA2
    Test class for NSGA2 method
